r. 719</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.457" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 457</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 5.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. V, 1, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 3, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.1.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 1, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.220" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 220</bibl>.<lb />2) name of the two inns of court in London: <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.19" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 19</bibl>. <cit><quote>T. garden,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.125" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 125</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>T. hall,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.223" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 223</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 3</bibl>.
